FEATURES:
	Global build mode:
		-Weather is always Sun
		-Time:  Won't get night while in build mode
		-No Drops from breaking Blocks
	User build mode:
		Switch between different inventorys for building and normal playing
		-Instant Block Break
		Place blocks in x height over the user
		-Godmode
		/top port
		Unlimited Items
		-No Pickups
		Wallbuilder
